#compdef pullDb loadDb refreshDb pullQuotesDb loadQuotesDb refreshQuotesDb viewDb viewLocalBpDb viewDevBpDb viewQatBpDb viewUatBpDb viewPreprodBpDb viewProdBpDb viewDevCtDb viewQatCtDb viewUatCtDb viewProdCtDb

# Completion for development environment database functions

_devenv_services() {
  local -a services
  services=(
    'bp:Broker Portal'
    'ct:Carrier Tracker'
  )
  _describe 'service' services
}

_devenv_envs() {
  local -a envs
  envs=(
    'local:Local environment'
    'dev:Development environment'
    'qat:QAT environment'
    'uat:UAT environment'
    'preprod:Pre-production environment'
    'prod:Production environment'
  )
  _describe 'environment' envs
}

_devenv_database_completion() {
  local context state state_descr line
  typeset -A opt_args

  case "$service" in
    pullDb)
      _message 'Pull broker portal database from dev'
      ;;
    loadDb)
      _message 'Load broker portal database locally'
      ;;
    refreshDb)
      _message 'Pull and load broker portal database'
      ;;
    pullQuotesDb)
      _message 'Pull carrier tracker database from dev'
      ;;
    loadQuotesDb)
      _message 'Load carrier tracker database locally'
      ;;
    refreshQuotesDb)
      _message 'Pull and load carrier tracker database'
      ;;
    viewDb)
      _arguments \
        '1:service:_devenv_services' \
        '2:environment:_devenv_envs' \
        && return 0
      ;;
    viewLocalBpDb)
      _message 'View local broker portal database'
      ;;
    viewDevBpDb)
      _message 'View dev broker portal database'
      ;;
    viewQatBpDb)
      _message 'View QAT broker portal database'
      ;;
    viewUatBpDb)
      _message 'View UAT broker portal database'
      ;;
    viewPreprodBpDb)
      _message 'View preprod broker portal database'
      ;;
    viewProdBpDb)
      _message 'View prod broker portal database'
      ;;
    viewDevCtDb)
      _message 'View dev carrier tracker database'
      ;;
    viewQatCtDb)
      _message 'View QAT carrier tracker database'
      ;;
    viewUatCtDb)
      _message 'View UAT carrier tracker database'
      ;;
    viewProdCtDb)
      _message 'View prod carrier tracker database'
      ;;
  esac
}

_devenv_database_completion "$@"
